ProcedureHelp.#cdata:
Syntax: PROC SGDESIGN SGD="SGD-file-specification" <option(s)>;
    DYNAMIC dynamic-var–1="assigned-value–1" <...dynamic-var–n="assigned-value-n">;

The SGDESIGN procedure produces a graph from one or more input SAS data sets and a user-defined 
ODS Graphics Designer (SGD) file. The SGD file is created with the SAS ODS Graphics Designer 
application.
